<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer for the Kingdom</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Jul 12, 2015 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
God of Hope,
</p>

 <p>
My lips say, <br></br>
“Thy Kingdom come, <br></br>
Thy will be done…,”
</p>

 <p>
But my heart says,
</p>

 <p>
“My will, <br></br>
my world, <br></br>
and my way.”
</p>

 <p>
How can I pray for your Kingdom, <br></br>
when I am not yet willing <br></br>
to relinquish my own?
</p>

 <p>
Loosen my grip on myself, <br></br>
that I may open my arms <br></br>
to embrace your vision <br></br>
for this world.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


